<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>An urgent hazmat operation is underway after a dangerous chemical spilled out of a train in Sydney.</p>

<p>Tonnes of liquid ammonium nitrate leaked from the goods train at the Enfield rail yarn in Greenacre.</p>

<p>New South Wales Fire and Rescue crews are on the scene. </p>

<p>The area is being evacuated and an exclusion zone and evacuation is being established. </p>

<p>More to come </p>
